        "# Mathematical preliminaries for deep learning\n",
        "\n",
        "## Scalars, vectors, matrices, tensors\n",
        "\n",
        "A scalar is a single value.\n",
        "A vector is an ordered list of values.\n",
        "A matrix is a 2D array.\n",
        "A tensor is a generalization to higher dimensions.\n",
        "\n",
        "In deep learning, dimensions encode meaning:\n",
        "\n",
        "1. Batch dimension\n",
        "2. Feature/channel dimension\n",
        "3. Optional sequence/time and spatial dimensions\n",
        "\n",
        "A shape mismatch error is usually a math-model mismatch, not just a coding bug."
